race.comment: After a myriad of scratchings keen on the prospects of NEVERENOUGHLEGO (10) who wasn't disgraced fresh over 1000m then missed a lip last time. Picked up well in the soft ground and hit the line hard. Fitter again and looks close to getting off the mark.  OF THE VIEW (8) has placed 4/5 starts to date and is long overdue. Returned from a spell with a sound on pace second last start over 1200m at Mildura. First try in soft ground but strips fitter and looks hard to beat off the low draw on best figures.  BRILLIANT BEAGLE (7) has ability and is racing well with two minor placings from four starts. Was a bit one paced over 1300m last time when on speed before fading for seventh over 1300m at Echuca. On the quick back-up and is right in the mix. ANALYTICAL (2) resumes on the back of a hit-out and has placed fresh. Will be winding up late.
race.rail_position: +4m from the 400m to the winning post, True Remainder. (Pent: 5.60)
